  "text": "Minku [CITATION_1] carries out a similar investigation, although with a more pragmatic emphasis than ours. A λ parameter in Online Bagging is used as a proxy for diversity, and diversity is maintained throughout the experiment, while we only enforce certain amounts of diversity on the initial concepts. The results are broadly consistent, although ours are specifically tailored to address our hypotheses regarding margins, diversity and adaptivity.",
